---
config:
  theme: white
  themeVariables:
    background: '#ffffff'
    primaryColor: '#ffffff'
    primaryTextColor: '#000000'
    lineColor: '#000000'
    secondaryColor: '#ffffff'
    tertiaryColor: '#ffffff'
    actorBorder: '#000000'
    actorTextColor: '#000000'
  look: classic
  mirrorActors: true
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Client as Client
    participant Route as AuthRoute
    participant Factory as FacebookAuthProviderFactory
    participant UC as LoginUseCase
    participant Provider as FacebookAuthProvider
    participant FB as Facebook OAuth Service
    participant DB as UserRepo / AccountRepo
    Client->>Route: POST /auth/login/facebook (code, redirect_uri)
    activate Route
    Route->>Factory: FacebookAuthProviderFactory(user_repo, account_repo, <br>storage_svc, client_id, client_secret, redirect_uri)
    Note right of Factory: Concrete factory instantiated<br>at the route layer
    Route->>UC: LoginUseCase(db_session, factory, token_svc)
    activate UC
    Route->>UC: await execute(payload)
    UC->>Factory: create_provider() [factory method]
    activate Factory
    Factory->>Provider: FacebookAuthProvider(user_repo, account_repo, storage_svc, client_id, client_secret, redirect_uri)
    Note right of Provider: Implements IAuthProvider + IOAuthProvider.<br>UseCase receives IAuthProvider only.
    Factory-->>UC: IAuthProvider
    deactivate Factory
    UC->>Provider: await authenticate(payload)
    activate Provider
    Note over Provider,FB: IOAuthProvider steps — encapsulated inside authenticate()
    Provider->>FB: get_access_token(code, redirect_uri)
    activate FB
    FB-->>Provider: access_token
    deactivate FB
    Provider->>FB: get_user_info(access_token)
    activate FB
    FB-->>Provider: OAuthUserInfo (facebook_id, email, name, avatar)
    deactivate FB
    Provider->>DB: resolve or create user + account record
    activate DB
    DB-->>Provider: user record
    deactivate DB
    Provider-->>UC: AuthResult(user_id, email, provider="facebook")
    deactivate Provider
    UC->>UC: await db_session.commit()
    UC-->>Route: AuthResult
    deactivate UC
    Route-->>Client: 200 OK
    deactivate Route